					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I consider them all my dear friends. I can’t imagine that any of them harbor bittersweet feelings of love for me...",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"大家都是重要的伙伴，很难想像她会对我抱持酸酸甜甜的好意。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
